reviewText: It was delivered early that's a good thing. The packaging was fine just the right size. the cover looks just like the advertisement. The DVD played with out a problem. but the animation and the way the DVD was put together was sloppy the animation on the cover was better than the DVD I would not buy this again and I would not recommend this to any one else.
Not what I expected at all.

Each of the sections were funny and fun to watch except the one with the gang rape of the young lady. The stupid boyfriend trusted a band member and then she was brutally done in. So lame. The other sections had an element of humor especially the part where a young lady was trying to prevent being electrocuted only to be done in other ways.
